item.title: FindGithubProfile
item.description: My project lets users search for any GitHub account by entering a username in the search bar. It fetches data from the GitHub API, displaying key info like the profile picture, name, bio, and repositories in a card. A ‘View Profile’ button allows users to quickly access the full GitHub profile.

item.title: HTML and CSS Projects
item.description: This repository showcases 10 unique projects developed using HTML and CSS. Each project highlights different aspects of frontend design and layout, ranging from responsive web pages to custom UI components.
